data.description: This beautiful traditional 5 bedroom, 3 bath home is nestled in the Legends Ranch Subdivision on a cul-de-sac. There are multiple attractive aspects to this house which are perfect for any family. The open-floor-plan kitchen looks out over an oversized island onto a formal-living area and breakfast nook with beautiful crown-molding and lots of natural sunlight. The open formal dining room can be entered immediately at the entrance of the home. Four of the five bedrooms are upstairs, including the spacious master suite, while the fifth bedroom is located downstairs as part of a guest suite. In addition to the four bedrooms, you can enjoy a large game room as well as a utility room all on the spacious second floor. Finally, one of the shining jewels of the house is the backyard, which has been meticulously crafted into a gorgeous garden including live vegetation to provide fruit and vegetables year round.
